lusion\">Delusion</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>27–29</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Djinni Summoning\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Djinni_Summoning\">Djinni Summoning</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"><p>2</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>30–39</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Fire Resistance\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Fire_Resistance\">Fire Resistance</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"><p>3</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>40–50</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Invisibility\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Invisibility\">Invisibility</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>51–55</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Protection\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Protection\">Protection +1, 5’ radius</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"><p>4</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>56–70</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Protection\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Protection\">Protection +1</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>71–72</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Regeneration\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Regeneration\">Regeneration</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>73–74</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Spell Storing\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Spell_Storing\">Spell Storing</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>75–80</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Spell Turning\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Spell_Turning\">Spell Turning</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>81–82</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Telekinesis\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Telekinesis\">Telekinesis</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"><p>5</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>83–88</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Water Walking\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Water_Walking\">Water Walking</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"><p>6</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>89–94</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Weakness\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Weakness\">Weakness</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>95–96</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Wishes\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Wishes\">Wishes, 1–2</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>97</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Wishes\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Wishes\">Wishes, 1–3</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>98</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of Wishes\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_Wishes\">Wishes, 2–4</a></p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"border-style:none;width:2em;text-align:center\"> </td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:4em;text-align:center\"><p>99–00</p></td><td style=\"border-style:none;width:8em\"><p><a title=\"Ring of X-Ray Vision\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ring_of_X-Ray_Vision\">X-Ray Vision</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br /><strong>Usage:</strong> All characters (unless noted).</p><p><strong>Activating:</strong> A ring’s magical effect is activated by placing it on a finger or thumb. Unless noted otherwise, a magical ring’s effect is continuously active and ends if the ring is removed.</p><p><strong>Multiple rings:</strong> A character can wear two magic rings—one on each hand. If more are worn, their magical effects do not function.</p><p><strong>Cursed rings:</strong> Cannot be “deactivated” by wearing more magical rings. </p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":900000,"name":"Rods, Staves, Wands","type":"text","_id":"ta4J1G7WdmsLMbE4","title":{"show":true,"lev