d\">Create Food</a></li><li><a title=\"Dispel Evil\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Dispel_Evil\">Dispel Evil</a></li><li><a title=\"Insect Plague\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Insect_Plague\">Insect Plague</a></li><li><a title=\"Quest (Remove Quest)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Quest_(Remove_Quest)\">Quest (Remove Quest)</a></li><li><a title=\"Raise Dead (Finger of Death)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Raise_Dead_(Finger_of_Death)\">Raise Dead (Finger of Death)</a></li></ol>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1},"flags":{}},{"sort":500000,"name":"Magic-User Spells","type":"text","_id":"zcaZpHS86nNkspWg","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<h2><span id=\"1st_Level\" class=\"mw-headline\">1st Level</span></h2><ol><li><a title=\"Charm Person\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Charm_Person\">Charm Person</a></li><li><a title=\"Detect Magic (MU)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Detect_Magic_(MU)\">Detect Magic</a></li><li><a title=\"Floating Disc\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Floating_Disc\">Floating Disc</a></li><li><a title=\"Hold Portal\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Hold_Portal\">Hold Portal</a></li><li><a title=\"Light (Darkness) (MU)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Light_(Darkness)_(MU)\">Light (Darkness)</a></li><li><a title=\"Magic Missile\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Magic_Missile\">Magic Missile</a></li><li><a title=\"Protection from Evil (MU)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Protection_from_Evil_(MU)\">Protection from Evil</a></li><li><a title=\"Read Languages\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Read_Languages\">Read Languages</a></li><li><a title=\"Read Magic\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Read_Magic\">Read Magic</a></li><li><a title=\"Shield\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Shield\">Shield</a></li><li><a title=\"Sleep\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Sleep\">Sleep</a></li><li><a title=\"Ventriloquism\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Ventriloquism\">Ventriloquism</a></li></ol><h2><span id=\"2nd_Level\" class=\"mw-headline\">2nd Level</span></h2><ol><li><a title=\"Continual Light (Continual Darkness)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Continual_Light_(Continual_Darkness)\">Continual Light (Continual Darkness)</a></li><li><a title=\"Detect Evil\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Detect_Evil\">Detect Evil</a></li><li><a title=\"Detect Invisible\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Detect_Invisible\">Detect Invisible</a></li><li><a title=\"ESP\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/ESP\">ESP</a></li><li><a title=\"Invisibility\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Invisibility\">Invisibility</a></li><li><a title=\"Knock\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Knock\">Knock</a></li><li><a title=\"Levitate\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Levitate\">Levitate</a></li><li><a title=\"Locate Object (MU)\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Locate_Object_(MU)\">Locate Object</a></li><li><a title=\"Mirror Image\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome.com/srd/index.php/Mirror_Image\">Mirror Image</a></li><li><a title=\"Phantasmal Force\" href=\"https://oldschoolessentials.necroticgnome