n:center\">–</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:5em;text-align:center\">–</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:5em;text-align:center\">–</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:3em;text-align:center\">10</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:3em;text-align:center\">90</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center\">450’ (150’)</td></tr></tbody></table><p>* Crew act as rowers, sailors, and fighters.</p><p>** May be piloted by unskilled characters.</p><h2><span id=\"Vessel_Combat_Stats\" class=\"mw-headline\">Vessel Combat Stats</span></h2><table style=\"width:95%;border-color:#444444;border-style:solid;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1px\"><thead><tr><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:6em;vertical-align:bottom\"><strong>Vessel</strong></td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center;vertical-align:bottom\"><strong>Maximum Mercenaries</strong></td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center;vertical-align:bottom\"><strong>Armour Class</strong></td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center;vertical-align:bottom\"><strong>Hull Points</strong></td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center;vertical-align:bottom\"><strong>Ram?</strong></td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center;vertical-align:bottom\"><strong>Catapults?</strong></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:6em\">Boat (river)</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center\">–</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center\">8 [11]</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center\">20–40</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center\">–</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:4em;text-align:center\">–</td></tr><tr><td style=\"border:none;padding:8px;width:6em\">Boat (sailing)</td><td style=\"border:none;padding:8p